Visual Studio 2022 Image Library

Use instructions

Images that have KnownMonikers are consumable by any Visual Studio component or extension via the Visual Studio Image Service. The same usage restrictions apply to all variations of a given image. As part of a visual language, the following images (or any part of the images) must be used in a manner consistent with the image name or concept description indicated below.

Read the Visual Studio 2022 Image Library EULA.
